Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来这儿太好了 健二前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.93,0:02:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,树 美极了 我要燃烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来这边 一起游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...那个...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 现在就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了? 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正在过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.23,0:02:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来这儿太好了 树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(138,131)\fs20\fad(650,900)}夏末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前辈也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了? 不开心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 去乘滑梯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不了 我想一个人呆在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙总是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...可以的话我们也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 顺便一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.37,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便顺便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海一起去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...不了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.27,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最怕滑梯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡说什么 连那超级漂移都不在话下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.89,0:03:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙雪喜欢蛮干 她的一贯风格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班人也很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的没关系吗 大家都请假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我硬请了带薪假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然店长一脸的不愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.03,0:03:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太耀眼了 现在仍觉得心脏快裂开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是看到了真子的泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.55,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就已经是二十一年的人生中最棒的夏日回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一生都忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正对我来说真子是高不可攀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多事真的要多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.88,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真心感谢池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过上次比赛我明白了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.96,0:04:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然给你添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我决定不放弃赛车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.75,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想你放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自命不凡罢了 什么碓冰山道最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是别人捧出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 拉不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用侧滑避开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.56,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那场比赛中 我重新认识到控车技术的深奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.77,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我明白现在放弃的话就等于半途而废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听你这么说我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做的事也算起了点作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.39,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还记得上次在湖畔的约定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以池谷先生可能有点误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说的并不是想做交易的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请要了我的处女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八点左右在初次和池谷先生相遇的招牌下等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再慢一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背后的胸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前辈...背后居然是个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太悲哀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子 拿一下球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高桥凉介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我扔了 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往哪儿扔啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么真子有高桥凉介的照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...能问个问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.26,0:07:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说过以前没和人交往过吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.64,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算没交往过 爱的人总有的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在想为什么没和他交往呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得真子这么可爱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝大多数男人都会趋之若鹜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会...哪有这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是做什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人...是车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时我还是高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概三年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和几位前辈去看赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时的我一无所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然间被一辆车的跑法给震撼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人的跑法 连我这外行都看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和别的车不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然有这么酷的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.39,0:08:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是就完全陷入了车手的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上去考了驾照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还硬是买了辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是忘我的练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想着开得好的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能稍微接近那人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动机不纯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.84,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想看那人的跑法 所以坚持去看比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可和那人连话都没说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.94,0:09:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己都不知道那算不算恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.04,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至不清楚思慕的到底他的人还是他的跑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过你是爱他的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾经的最爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了? 这种痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 不问就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉真子离我好遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子一直思慕的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.25,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然是群马地区NO.1的超级巨星...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高桥凉介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么她向往的车会是FC
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.84,0:10:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了了 不可能赢得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥终于要出手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和那辆秋名的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陪我试试如何? 启介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的最快理论 实践给你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开心的一塌糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和女孩去游泳原来这么开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是几乎都和健二前辈在一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子和沙雪是最棒的呢 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真会见风使舵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.31,0:12:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前阵子不是还在说车手不需要女人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她们俩不一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她们俩穿比基尼的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使灼伤了眼也不舍得移开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太耀眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不舍得沙雪那晃动的咪咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但还是真子好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身材出众 对吧 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.61,0:12:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这心不在焉的反应算什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.61,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得你有点郁闷 和真子吵架了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.29,0:12:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没那回事 只是有点累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这时候来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 店长 今天硬是请了假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.86,0:13:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 你还年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶尔也该挥洒一下青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年纪不小了别光沉迷于车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都担心你找不到女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的天使是叫真子吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺利吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.31,0:13:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...看来是不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.03,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我果然还是高攀不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说什么丧气话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着 池谷 女人其实...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.69,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别...真的没关系了店长 我已经放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.99,0:13:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能赢得过高桥凉介啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事? 总算是追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥的FC明明没改动过 为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的最快理论...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加入了新的数据就能进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等着吧 秋名的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个理论完成之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是将你名字列入失败者名单之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好难受 心跳得太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办? 现在就已经这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生来了的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋啊 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你对女人一无所知啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别呃了 听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果以前交往的是高桥凉介那就另当别论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事只要是小女孩都有过的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和思慕电视里的演员没什么区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷静头脑想一想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.98,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因为真子选择的并非高桥凉介而是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表示她拿出勇气下的决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为相信你才会毫不隐瞒地说出那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不懂吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别总是执迷于你那无聊的自卑感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恋慕就是要包容对方的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓的爱与恋不正是如此吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么? 八点?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 已经过了三十分钟啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.54,0:16:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.35,0:16:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎么狂飙去横川也要一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子不可能还等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事不去怎么知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.28,0:16:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不去的话就炒了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.57,0:17:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使劲飙 池谷 你也是个车手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种时候才需要拼命地跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.79,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话是这么说...来不及了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.28,0:17:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店长说得对 我实在太笨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子这么好的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死也不会再有机会遇上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为什么不坦率点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫佐藤真子 打我电话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把处女献给池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八点左右在初次和池谷先生相遇的招牌下等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子一直都是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我...而我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脚开始痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌凉鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.22,0:19:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子 我并不怎么想去旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.92,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扪心自问...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想什么呢 不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何我只想见到真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神啊 求求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再给我一次机会 别将我的天使带离人间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堵车? 出事故了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会...神啊...你怎么能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.52,0:19:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.19,0:20:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也不穿凉鞋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.79,0:24:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了拓海 那束花是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.50,0:24:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.51,0:24:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏木送的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.38,0:24:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.88,0:24:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.77,0:24:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,观众女孩送给如今群马车手中无人不知...
